Package org.wso2.transport.http.netty.listener

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CustomHttpContentCompressor
    Custom Http Content Compressor to handle the content-length and transfer encoding.
    Http2SourceHandler
    HTTP2SourceHandler read the HTTP/2 binary frames sent from client through the channel.
    Http2SourceHandlerBuilder
    HTTP2SourceHandlerBuilder is used to build the HTTP2SourceHandler.
    Http2ToHttpFallbackHandler
    Http2ToHttpFallbackHandler is responsible for fallback from http2 to http when http2 upgrade fails.
    Http2WithPriorKnowledgeHandler
    Http2WithPriorKnowledgeHandler handles the requests received directly in HTTP/2 without attempting an upgrade from HTTP/1.x.
    HttpAccessLoggingHandler
    Logging handler for HTTP access logs.
    HttpServerChannelInitializer
    A class that responsible for build server side channels.
    HTTPTraceLoggingHandler
    A custom LoggingHandler for the HTTP wire logs
    MaxEntityBodyValidator
    Responsible for validating request entity body size before sending it to the application.
    OCSPResponseBuilder
    A class for generating OCSP response.
    RequestDataHolder
    RequestDataHolder holds data fields of the request which might be useful later in the message flow.
    ServerBootstrapConfiguration
    A class represents Server Bootstrap configurations.
    ServerConnectorBootstrap
    ServerConnectorBootstrap is the heart of the HTTP Server Connector.
    SourceHandler
    A Class responsible for handle incoming message through netty inbound pipeline.
    SourceHandlerErrorHandler
    Handle all the errors related to source-handler.
    SslHandshakeCompletionHandlerForServer
    A handler to check whether TLS handshake has been completed.
    UriAndHeaderLengthValidator
    Responsible for validating the request before sending it to the application.
    WebSocketFramesBlockingHandler
    This Handler is responsible for issuing frame by frame when the WebSocket connection is asked to read next frame when autoRead is set to false.
    WebSocketServerHandshakeHandler
    WebSocket handshake handler for carbon transports.
    WebSocketSourceHandler
    This class handles all kinds of WebSocketFrames after connection is upgraded from HTTP to WebSocket.
